                java.lang.String periodicityEmission,
                long activeSubscriptions)
        Constructs a Magazine object with the specified parameters.
        pre:
        The id, name, url, pages, publication, value, and pagesRead parameters must not be null. The category parameter must be a valid index corresponding to a Category value. The activeSubscriptions parameter must be a non-negative integer.
        post:
        A new Magazine object is created with the given parameters.
        Parameters:
        id - the ID of the magazine
        name - the name of the magazine
        url - the URL of the magazine
        pages - the total number of pages in the magazine
        publication - the publication date of the magazine
        value - the value of the magazine
        pagesRead - the number of pages already read in the magazine
        category - the category of the magazine
        periodicityEmission - the periodicity of the magazine's emission
        activeSubscriptions - the number of active subscriptions for the magazine
